Kyle.Anderson@northbaychrysler.com>
Sent: Wednesday, May 1, 2024 1:44 PM
To: claims <claims@canadageneral.ca>
Subject: LESTER MIANSKUM
 
Good Afternoon!

Pleas see the attached estimate for Lester and Samantha Mianskum. Vehicle was brought in for a check engine light. After diagnostic the vehicle does have a misfire. Technician would like to replace spark plugs and coil #1. Also upon inspection Technician found the LR wheel bearing to be loose and have some play and the rear knuckle bushings are failing and require replacement.  Please advise if there is any coverage for this repair and we can order parts and get the vehicle back to the customer. Thank you!

Regards,
Kyle Anderson
Service Advisor
North Bay Chrysler
